---
title: Spanish Steak Salad with Roasted Red Peppers and Rosemary-Garlic Vinaigrette
description: Oven-roasting takes garlic from bold and pungent to sweet and mellow. Here, garlic and rosemary are roasted together to create the base for an unbeatable vinaigrette. Drizzled over sliced steak, roasted red peppers, and tangy goat cheese, salads don't get much better than this.
